Sentencas: Impedance spectroscopy (IS) is an effective tool for the analysis of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) and solid oxide electrolysis cell (SOEC) performance.
Titulo: Impedance spectroscopy analysis inspired by evolutionary programming as a diagnostic tool for SOEC and SOFC

Sentencas: The challenge using this characterization tool lies within the analysis method.
Titulo: Impedance spectroscopy analysis inspired by evolutionary programming as a diagnostic tool for SOEC and SOFC

Sentencas: Impedance spectroscopy genetic programming (ISGP) is a novel analysis technique for impedance spectroscopy data.
Titulo: Impedance spectroscopy analysis inspired by evolutionary programming as a diagnostic tool for SOEC and SOFC

Sentencas: The ISGP utilizes evolutionary programming techniques for finding the most suitable distribution function of relaxation times (DFRT).
Titulo: Impedance spectroscopy analysis inspired by evolutionary programming as a diagnostic tool for SOEC and SOFC

Sentencas: This approach leads toward a better analysis of impedance spectroscopy results as compared to other analysis tools such as equivalent circuits or deconvolution techniques.
Titulo: Impedance spectroscopy analysis inspired by evolutionary programming as a diagnostic tool for SOEC and SOFC

Sentencas: In this work, SOFC and SOEC were examined during operation by IS measurements and the results were analyzed using ISGP.
Titulo: Impedance spectroscopy analysis inspired by evolutionary programming as a diagnostic tool for SOEC and SOFC

Sentencas: The aim of this work is to show examples of DFRT models which reflect the physical processes occurring during the operation.
Titulo: Impedance spectroscopy analysis inspired by evolutionary programming as a diagnostic tool for SOEC and SOFC

Sentencas: It is demonstrated that despite the low impedance (in the m Omega range) and the narrow available bandwidth, ISGP can provide consistent DFRT models.
Titulo: Impedance spectroscopy analysis inspired by evolutionary programming as a diagnostic tool for SOEC and SOFC
